Rajiram's crew included many [[human]]s from the Nelanther Isles.
Also serving in his crew were [[minotaur]]s, [[goblin]]s, and [[oni]].

Among the notable members of his crew were [[Boff Badcrack]] the [[hill giant]] [[Mouth of Grolantor]] and [[Sláturhaust]] the [[storm giant]] [[quintessent]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Mysterious Isle|4}} 

Rajiram's followers were completely devoted to him; they feared his anger more than they feared death.{{Cite adventurers league/Reclamation|10}} He gave [[frost brand]] [[scimitar]]s to the pirates he liked the most.{{Cite adventurers league/The Ark of the Mountains|15}}
